description: Just about as simple as a coffee table can get, but it's still an attractive piece of furniture.

name: Stepping Stones
description: Great for stepping, but watch your balance!

name: Double Lamp Post
description: A post with two glowing lamps, it's two lights for the post of one.

description: A big rug of spun fluffy fiber, it feels soft and tickly against your skin.

description: A big rug of spun fluffy fiber, it feels soft and tickly against your skin.

description: A velvety green rug lined in gold, this would look nice just about anywhere.

name: Rustic Brick Fireplace
description: Handcrafted clay bricks stacked in the same way as the fireplaces of old, keep your home warm and toasty with some oldschool aesthetic.

name: Stone Oven
description: An old stone oven, just like your granny might have used. It's heated by burning logs, but still does a great job baking anything.

name: Watermelon Couch
description: The unusual design in this red couch's cushions is meant to mimic the seeds of a watermelon slice, how fun!

name: Oak Kitchen Cabinet
description: A cabinet of beautiful stained oak sourced from the Northern Region, this would look good in any kitchen.

name: Metal Standing Mirror
description: A long body mirror set in a heavy iron frame, it's pretty heavy but certainly sturdy.

name: Rainbow Poster
description: It's like your own personal rainbow, ready to add a streak of color to your room.

name: Modest Teal Fridge
description: Just a standard model fridge. Nothing special, but it looks quaint and it gets the job done.

name: Insignia Emblem Desk
description: A wooden desk with a mystical insignia carved into it. It's said that the symbol holds mystical properties, but at the very least it looks pretty neat.

name: Light Green Lined Wooden Table
description: The green border of this table denotes it as a medical desk, often found in hospitals and doctor's offices.

name: Purple Mat Desk
description: An otherwise unremarkable wooden desk, it comes topped with a soft purple mat that is easy on the elbows when you're doing a spot of writing.

name: Oak Kitchen Sink Counter
description: A countertop of beautiful stained oak sourced from the Northern Region, this would look good in any kitchen.

name: Oak Kitchen Island
description: A kitchen island of beautiful stained oak sourced from the Northern Region, this would look good in any kitchen.

name: Rustic Kitchen Counter
description: A countertop in the style of the old cottage homes found throughout the Eastern Region.

name: Miyeon's Amateur Painting
description: Miyeon attempted to paint the park fountain. She... Didn't do very good. But still, 'A' for effort! Oh, and an 'A' for Angel!

name: Golden Glass Statue
description: Is the glass gold? Is the gold glass?? Who cares, because either way this statue is super fancy.

name: Giant Golden Time Turner
description: Time is money, gold is money. This golden time turner, therefore, is double money.

name: Golden Sand Castle
description: The fanciest sand castle you're ever going to build, that's for sure.

name: Fiddle-Leaf Fern
description: A common plant that grows all over the place, adventurers swear to the tastiness of this fern when roasted over an open fire.

name: Red Butterfly Couch
description: The back of this couch resembles the wavy wings of a butterfly. Whether that was intentional or not, the couch is stilly really fancy.

name: Magenta Chaise Couch
description: One of the fancier pieces of furniture to come from the Great City's experimental craftsmen.

name: Teal Sectional Couch
description: A mighty four cushion sectional couch, it can fit into a corner or even work to close off an area room.

name: Brown Leather Couch
description: Don't worry, it's made out of an artificial leather. It looks just like the real deal, and no animals were harmed making it! Neat.

name: Fancy Blue Dining Chair
description: Striking blue wood, from King Minos's royal forest, paired with smooth velvet seat cushions. Oh yeah, this is fancy stuff.

name: Carnival Balloons
description: Balloons commemorating the great Withergate carnival.

name: Withergate Balloons
description: A monstrous assortment of balloons.

name: Monster Mouth Chair
description: Take a load off your tired teeth- er, your tired FEET- with this monster chair.

name: Monster Mouth Table
description: Table monsters aren't such bad guys. They might look scary, but they really just want to be a table.

name: Monster Mouth Couch
description: It looks bit forboding, maybe, but it's still pretty comfortable.

name: Monster Mouth Wardrobe
description: This wardrobe hungers... FOR YOUR CLOTHES!

name: Monster Mouth Bed
description: Forget the bed bugs, make sure the bed doesn't bite!

name: Monster Mouth End Table
description: A great end table to store your personal effects... just, uh, watch out for the teeth.

name: Gothic Couch
description: You're not sure what leather this couch has been upholstered in, but whatever it is it seems to reflect not even the brightest of lights.

name: Gothic Chaise Couch
description: A couch in the favored style of Withergate's most socially (and financially) affluent Demons. This one is just a reproduction made with materials more suited to a mere peasant... like you!

name: Gothic Hutch
description: You can keep all sorts of stuff in this... plates, cups, bats, extra fangs... whatever you want, really.

name: Pumpkin Chair
description: As delightfully orange as a real pumpkin, and much more comfy to sit on.

name: Pumpkin Lamp
description: A tiny pumpkin with a lamp light inserted into it. Great for lighting up a spooky midnight walk, or maybe just your bedroom.

name: Pumpkin Couch
description: Sit your rumpkin down on the pumpkin... just watch out of the eyes.

name: Pumpkin Rug
description: You can't always walk through the pumpkin patch, but you can at least walk on a pumpkin. In rug form, that is.

name: Pumpkin Table
description: A ghoulishly carved table bedecked with a flowing pumpkin tablecloth.

name: Pumpkin Wardrobe
description: Keeps your clothes nice and pumpkin-fresh.

name: Pumpkin Bed
description: Oh yeah, this thing definitely has a monster underneath it. No doubt.

name: Pumpkin Nightstand
description: Ah, another table for your to store valuble pumpkins upon. How lucky.

name: Purple Wooden Square Desk
description: Made of wood cut from the trees of Withergate forest, it's rather eerie looking desk but just as sturdy and reliable as any other.

name: Purple Wooden Chair
description: A simple ordinary chair, made out of haunted purple wood.

name: Purple Stump
description: A stump of a strange purple tree. It'll make a good stool, if nothing else.

name: Purple Book Stack
description: A stack of old books covering topics on fishing. It's nothing you don't already know, but they'd make an interesting looking decoration.

name: Purple Eye Wall Lantern
description: A lantern in the shape of a big purple eye. It's pretty wild, but totally not out of place in your typical monster home.

name: Purple Round Stool
description: A comfortable little stool.

name: Purple Wall Shelf
description: Made of wood taken from the haunted Withergate forest. We can't guarantee it will be ghost-free.

name: Batty Boxes
description: Cardboard shipping boxes used by Withergate's official courier service, their bat logo is iconically emblazoned upon each box.

name: Cat Eye Flower
description: An eerie flower, the "eye" gives off a dull shine in the light. Definitely native to Withergate's haunted forests.

name: Pumpkin Trio
description: A stack of little pumpkins, ready to come visit you at your home.

name: Small Mystic's Bookshelf
description: Small shelves packed with just a few of the magical essentials any mystic would find themselves needing.

name: Magic Wand Holder
description: Magic wands should always be kept neat and orderly.

name: Pawn Chess Piece
description: While you may think there's not much a lone pawn can do, no serious chess player would ever carelessly underestimate one.

name: Crate of Tentacles
description: "Go eat a crate of tentacles" is a popular saying among Demonkind, but who knew they meant it literally...

name: Candy Bowls
description: Cute glass pumpkins full of tantalizing, irresistible candy. Try to contain yourself.

name: Insect Buddy
description: Who says insects can't be your friend? This little fella makes for a great six-legged buddy.

name: Glow in the Dark Stars
description: Carved from polished stone and then enchanted, the glow of these little stars are best observed in the dark.

name: Mystical Fire Pit
description: A magical flame that burns without giving off any heat, as if it were some sort of phantom fire.

name: Toy Vending Machine
description: A machine full of toys. Put a ticket in, crank the knob and out comes a prize!

name: Baby Pumpkin Stack
description: An absolutely adorable stack of lil' baby pumpkins.

name: Fake Eyeball
description: Eww, an eyeball!! Oh, whew. It's just made out of rubber.

name: Ghost In Pumpkin
description: A mischevious ghost, it seems set on haunting this little pumpkin.

name: Grape Soda Pop
description: A fizzy purple drink, it's got all natural flavors and an absolute bucketload of sugar.

name: Soda Can
description: The necessary vessel for soda storage.

name: Slice of Cherry Pie
description: Wait, where's the rest of the pie?!

name: Candy Corn
description: Perhaps the most controversial of all the candies, it's said you aren't a true Withergatian unless you love this stuff.

name: Party Leftovers
description: So maybe you didn't clean up the junk food from last night's party... but who said the party ended?

name: Cutting Board with Lemon
description: A solid cutting board of oak, it's ready to see some action.

name: Red Mug
description: A red glazed ceramic mug, it holds just about any liquid you could think of.

name: Red High Heels
description: Withergate high fashion swears by these curiously high heeled shoes, though they're far too uncomfortable for you to ever try giving a go.

name: Red Rose Bouquet
description: A bundle of bright red roses. Though it may seem like they were bundled without much thought, they were actually placed quite meticulously.

name: Blue Rose Bouquet
description: A bundle of bright blue roses. Though it may seem like they were bundled without much thought, they were actually placed quite meticulously.

name: Violet Vase
description: Blown of glass and tinted dark violet, this vase keeps water nice and cool for any flowers kept inside.

name: Green Neon Light
description: A flashing green neon light to illuminate even the spookiest of spooky nights.

name: Orange Bat Wall Lantern
description: Go ahead, go absolutely batty for this awesome wall light. It's alright.

name: Blue Skull Wall Lantern
description: Only a real bonehead would pass up this gnarly skull wall light.

name: Wicked Candelabra
description: No haunted mansion would be complete without one of these hanging in its foyer.

name: Wicked Wall Lantern
description: A lantern of heavy black iron and blood red glass, it's not hard to see why it's called "wicked".

name: Princess Vanity Table
description: Just because you don't live in a castle doesn't mean you can't live like a princess.

name: Pink Shell Chair
description: Shell chairs might look a little odd, but they're engineered especially to be comfortable. You'll never sit in a better chair!

name: Bat Poster
description: A poster depicting a wicked bat, flying in front of some sort of sword. Looks like it's an advertisement for some old concert that took place in Withergate.

name: Fortune Teller Poster
description: A poster, advertising Withergate's resident fortune teller. It big ornate font it reads "Come meet the mystery of your future, today. No refunds".

name: Red T Window
description: A dramatically long and narrow window, it would go a long way in making your home feel like a gothic mansion.

name: Yellow T Window
description: A dramatically long and narrow window, it would go a long way in making your home feel like a gothic mansion.

name: Blue Wooden Square Table
description: A wooden table, hit with a fresh coat of blue paint. It's ready to hold whatever you'd like on it.

name: Wood Floor Tile
description: Wooden tiles specially treated to work as flooring.

name: Stone Floor Tile
description: Stone cut to uniform tiles, these would make an excellent pathway or floor.

name: Workshop Floor Tile
description: Stone tiles set tightly together, making them easy to sweep after a crafting project.

name: Wooden Plank Floor Tile
description: Wood processed into planks for a pleasantly smooth surface.

name: Brick Floor Tile
description: Classic red brick, sturdy and reliable.

name: White Stone Floor Tile
description: Clean and classy, these tiles are suited to a distinguished decorator.

name: Patterned Floor Tile
description: Thin stone tiles carefully lined in a pattern, this style of floor is very popular in the Eastern region.

name: Oak Plank Floor Tile
description: Dark wooden planks to add a dramatic flair to your space.

name: Apple Tree Seeds
description: These tiny seeds will sprout into a bountiful apple tree once planted.

name: Orange Tree Seeds
description: These tiny seeds will sprout into a bountiful orange tree once planted.

name: Blueberry Tree Seeds
description: These tiny seeds will sprout into a bountiful blueberry tree once planted.

description: These tiny seeds will sprout into a bountiful strawberry tree once planted.

name: Festive Orange Tree Seeds
description: These tiny seeds will sprout into a bountiful orange tree once planted.

description: Is it just you, or is this seed bag... growling?

description: Mean seeds that grow easily in the angry soils of Withergate.

description: These tree seeds twinkle with tiny glimmers of fairy dust.

name: Nectar-ine Tree Seeds
description: Seeds dripping with sweet, sticky nectar.

description: Tree nuts that faintly shimmer a myriad of different colors, they'll grow into fantastic Elven trees once planted.

name: Rex's Cap
description: Rex's head has been sorely missing this mining hat, better get it back to him quick.

name: Topi's Notebook
description: Topi said it was a notebook of schoolwork, but it looks like it's mostly a bunch of doodles.

name: Peter's Lure
description: Seems like just an ordinary lure, I wonder what's so lucky about it?

name: Joke Book
description: A book of corny jokes.

name: Jun's Flower
description: Jun asked me to plant these around Sun Haven.

name: Meat

name: Glorite Crystal
description: A crystal that thrums with energy, it feels much heavier than it looks.

name: Toolbox
description: A rusty toolbox packed full of random tools for all sorts of different crafts.

name: Amanda's Book
description: Looks like a novel about a man and a horse, several pages have been dog-eared.

name: Albert's Sword
description: An old copper sword.

name: Medicine
description: Wornhardt needs this for his patient.

name: Arnold's Shirt
description: It's been stitched up so many times that even the stitches have stitches.

name: Back Scratcher
description: Great for scratching all of those hard-to-reach spots.

name: Cushion
description: Stuffed full of bouncy wool, this should keep anyone's bottom comfy on even the hardest ground.

name: Hand Mirror
description: Looks like this mirror has seen a lot of time at the bottom of the briny deep... did Honey find it in a sunken ship?!

name: Horseshoe
description: Horses wear shoes, but how come they don't wear socks?

name: Lavender Candle
description: It reeks of sickly-sweet lavender, yet you can't resist smelling it.

name: Ribbon
description: A silky soft length of ribbon, Arianella has outdone herself yet again.

name: Tape
description: "9 out of 10 dorks choose Harry's Spectacle-Mending Tape, perfect for all matters of mending broken eyewear".

name: Trusty Compass
description: Each of the cardinal directions has been replaced with the word "adventure".

name: Sack of Treasure
description: A burlap sack splitting at the seams with all sorts of treasure.

name: Seal of Sun Haven
description: A crest bearing the sigil of Sun Haven, Lucia enchanted it with a spell to aid mana regeneration. Permanently increases your max mana by 10.

name: Soul Sap
description: Viscous sap drained from a soul sap tree, it feels slightly tingly to the touch.

name: Great City Poster
description: A poster depicting the bustling streets of the Great City, Vaan wrote a message on the back.

name: Stone of Tongues
description: An enchanted stone that can translate any language, or at least the legends claim.

name: Charcoal
description: A piece of sooty charcoal. When it comes to writing, it'll work better than nothing.

name: Bird's Nest
description: Looks like the birds who made this nest moved out awhile ago.

name: Glass Jar
description: A simple jar of glass, you could put all sorts of things in it.

name: Hoof Polish
description: Brightly colored polish. It's like nail polish only, you know, for hooves.

name: Illusory Tonic
description: A glass cask full of a sparkling, swirling potion. It actually looks really delicious.

name: Moonsight Potion
description: A bottle of thin, watery liquid. It doesn't look very assuming, but apparently it's quite potent.

name: Nutrient Salve

name: Citrus Rub
description: A powder made out of the dried peels of tangy citrus fruits, tastebuds love it and bugs can't stand it.

name: Pollen
description: Fine granules of pollen, hand-picked by Beeanaca for premium quality.

name: Enchanted Soul Sap
description: Iris has enchanted this sap, augmenting its mysterious magical properties.

name: Bag of Kitten Nip
description: A mixture of dried herbs, it smells quite strange but apparently kittens love the stuff. Who could have lost it?

name: Medical Glove
description: A glove made out of some kind of smooth, squeaky material. Who could have lost it?

name: Lost Letter
description: This lost letter should be returned to the mail carrier.

name: Reading Glasses
description: A slightly dusty pair of reading glasses. Who could have lost it?

name: Sun Haven Library Book
description: The first page is stamped SUN HAVEN PUBLIC LIBRARY.

name: Eastern Bangle
description: The colors represent a Region in the east, and a piece of molten metal looks stuck to the normally smooth edge of the bangle. Who could have lost it?

name: Lost Toy
description: A cute toy, but it's not for you. Who could have lost it?

name: Grime Covered Magic Charm
description: A cute toy, but it's not for you. Who could have lost it?

description: A cute toy, but it's not for you. Who could have lost it?

description: A cute toy, but it's not for you. Who could have lost it?

name: Discolored Fishing Lure
description: A cute toy, but it's not for you. Who could have lost it?

name: Dragon Chow
description: Kitty's special baby dragon chow. It doesn't look very appetizing, but then again, you're not a baby dragon.

name: Dragon Trap
description: It's a box. It's literally just a box. But maybe it will do the trick?

name: Solon Order Form
description: An order form for dozens of pieces of equipment. Solon must be able to work fast to complete orders as big as these!

name: Chunky Grouper
description: A fat, oily grouper. Most anglers throw them back, as they make a poor meal. Unless you're a baby dragon, that is.

name: Pen Pal Quill
description: Permanently gain 2 community tokens every morning.

name: Lost Cart Wheel
description: The wheel to Clive's wagon. It must have broken off on the rough wilderness terrain.

name: Luke's Stylin' Honey
description: Honey infused with herbs and plants to form a gel that keeps hair looking fresh - plus it tastes great!

name: Broken Branches
description: These branches look oddly similar to Elios's mighty wings.

name: Pile of Snow
description: Not a hard resource to find in winter. What kind of sculpture could you make with this?

name: Broken Cobblestone
description: Two pieces of cobblestone that, of all things, look exactly like Elios's eyes.

name: Gorwin's Gift
description: A masterfully cut gem, shaped into the emblem of Sun Haven. A wonderful gift from Gorwin and an offering of peace.

name: Ancient Nel'Varian Text
description: Ancient Nel'Varian text, bound in a protective leather cover. Surely Amanda won't notice it's missing...

name: Totally Not Fake Nel'Varian Text
description: THIS WILL DEFINITELY TRICK AMANDA

name: Bernard's Big Bundle
description: A TON of supplies - all gifted to you from the citizens of Sun Haven!

name: Sun Dragon Scale
description: Glistens like polished copper in the light of the sun - and it's harder than mithril.

name: Moon Dragon Scale
description: This titanic scale does not reflect light, but rather seems to reject it all together.

description: A recording of Claude's performance taken from the music festival.

description: A record of Wesley's song, for you to play whenever you'd like.

name: Kai Record
description: A record of Kai's song, for you to play whenever you'd like.

name: Vivi Record
description: A record of Vivi's song, for you to play whenever you'd like.

name: Miyeon Record
description: A record of Miyeon's song, for you to play whenever you'd like.

name: Shang Record
description: A record of Shang's song, for you to play whenever you'd like.

name: Lucius' Record
description: A record of Lucius' song, for you to play whenever you'd like.

name: Pomegranate of Power
description: A legendary trinket, made by an ancient people. It contains the essence of a blessed pomegranate and passes a small bit of that power onto its holder.

name: Warrior's Pauldron
description: Said to have been smithed by a legendary armorer, wielding this pauldron makes you feel as indomitable as the mountains.

name: Golden Star Gear
description: This strange gear is undoubtedly very old, yet it looks as if it were still newly made. Where did it come from, and how did it end up in a cave?

name: Ceremonial Dagger
description: A golden dagger with a blood red ruby set on its pommel. Whatever the purpose of this dagger was, it's definitely seen plenty of use.

name: Fighter's Crest
description: A crest said to have been worn by a legendary fighter. Whether the legends are true or not, wearing the crest increases your combat potency.

name: Sapphire Wisp
description: An elemental wisp, hardened into an unnaturally smooth gem of sapphire. Possessing it increases one's passion for battle.

name: Ruby Wisp
description: An elemental wisp, hardened into an unnaturally smooth gem of ruby. Possessing it increases one's fortitude and very life essence.

name: Letter From Lucia
description: A handwritten decree of peace and understanding, scribed by Lucia herself. Despite its hasty drafting on the battlefield, the Archmage's penmanship is without equal.

name: Claude's Concerto
description: The original copy of Claude's famous concerto. It bears the composer's own signature, written in a blood red ink.

name: Expensive Gift
description: A gift wrapped with shiny, expensive looking paper. Whoever wrapped this wanted to make a statement!

name: Floral Gift
description: A gift wrapped in paper with beautiful flower patterns intertwining endlessly. A small charm hangs off the bow.

name: Music Note Gift
description: A gift wrapped in paper printed with little music notes all over it. It seems to be from Claude... but it's too cute to come from him, right?

name: Fancy Gift
description: A sharply wrapped gift in fancy paper, topped with a blood red bow ribbon. You get the impression that the gift giver didn't wrap this themselves... maybe a servant?

name: Newspaper Gift
description: A gift wrapped in some old newspapers, instead of gift wrap. One of the headlines reads "SUN HAVEN OUTSIDER SPOTTED IN WITHERGATE".

name: Leaf Gift
description: A gift wrapped in a large, soft leaf. You've never seen a leaf quite like this before, someone must have grown it just for this occasion.

name: Painted Gift
description: A gift wrapped in hand-painted paper. Very thoughtful!

name: Kitty Gift
description: A gift wrapped in flashy pink paper, covered in sprinkles and and pawprints. The gift tag reads "to XX, nya!". It obviously came from Kitty.

name: Little Girl's Gift
description: A gift wrapped in paper normally meant for a young girl. Whoever wrapped it must have only had this on hand.

name: Firebolt Gift
description: A gift wrapped in red paper with blazing fireballs printed across it. The bow is expertly tied to resemble Sun Haven's sun crest.

name: Homemade Gift
description: White paper that was turned into gift wrap. Despite the wrapper's best efforts, it's still smudged here and there with smithery soot.

name: Burlap Gift
description: Someone forgot to wrap their gift and instead elected to toss it into a burlap sack. "SHIELD POLISH" is printed on the side of the sack.

name: Bowed Gift
description: This gift isn't even wrapped, but dramatically topped with a single bow ribbon. You have a feeling that the wrapper wasn't being lazy, but rather was trying to grab your attention.

name: White Gift
description: A gift wrapped in fancy white wrapping paper. Is it just you, or does it kind of smell like the inside of a doctor's office?

name: Impeccable Gift
description: A gift wrapped in shiny paper, the wrap job is impeccable. Whoever is responsible for this must be especially skilled at planning.

name: Traditional Gift
description: A gift wrapped in simple paper, with colored strings that represent a bunch of obscure, boring Nel'Varian traditions.

name: Driftwood Gift
description: A gift wrapped in scraps of old ship sails and fishing nets. It's covered in sand.

name: Poorly Wrapped Gift
description: A crudely wrapped gift, whoever wrapped this wasn't very good at taking their time... or keeping their temper in check.

name: Moon Print Gift
description: A gift wrapped in a paper stamped with... a lot of moons. Like, a LOT of moons.

name: Celestial Runes Gift
description: A gift wrapped in sparkling golden runes of the Everbeyond. It's almost too pretty to open...

name: Tiger Print Gift
description: A gift wrapped in tiger paw paper. The ribbons look suspiciously as if they were cut with a sword...

name: Farming Skill Tome
description: A mystical tome imbued with the very essence of farming. Reading its pages will impart increased farming prowess and experience.

name: Exploration Skill Tome
description: A mystical tome imbued with the very essence of exploration. Reading its pages will impart increased exploration prowess and experience.

name: Mining Skill Tome
description: A mystical tome imbued with the very essence of mining. Reading its pages will impart increased mining prowess and experience.

name: Combat Skill Tome
description: A mystical tome imbued with the very essence of combat. Reading its pages will impart increased combat prowess and experience.

name: Fishing Skill Tome
description: A mystical tome imbued with the very essence of fishing. Reading its pages will impart increased fishing prowess and experience.

name: Elixir of Farming
description: An elixir brewed with the essence of cultivation and growth. It expands one's understanding of Farming when consumed.

name: Elixir of Exploration
description: An elixir brewed with the essence of the untamed wilderness. It expands one's understanding of Exploration when consumed.

name: Elixir of Mining
description: An elixir brewed with the essence of the deep earth. It expands one's understanding of Mining when consumed.

name: Elixir of Combat
description: An elixir brewed with the essence of battle and victory. It expands one's understanding of Combat when consumed.

name: Elixir of Fishing
description: An elixir brewed with the essence of patience and fish bait. It expands one's understanding of Fishing when consumed.

name: Vacuumulus
description: Emits a powerful shockwave around you, dealing damage to surrounding enemies and rocks.

name: Cataclysm
description: Transform into a spinning ball, granting massive movement speed and causing heavy damage to all enemies you collide with during this time.

name: Rain Cloud
description: Summon a cloud that waters any crops it travels over.

name: Earthquake
description: Shake up the earth, instantly tilling land in an area around you.

name: Aegis
description: Increases Armor of all players on the same map and heals them over time.

name: Fireball
description: Fires a blast of flames, damaging and burning enemies.

name: Fire Beam
description: Fires a sustained beam of energy, dealing damage to all enemies hit.

name: Bubble Net
description: Create an air bubble that floats forward, magically catching any fish that it travels over.

name: Chain Lightning
description: Shoots a bolt of lightning at an enemy, damaging them, and then jumping to additional nearby enemies.

name: Shadow Rush
description: Tap into your demonic ferocity, increasing your movement speed by 60% for 10 seconds.

name: Miracle
description: Call upon an angelic miracle, restoring 15 Health <color=#39CCFF>plus</color> 15% of your Maximum Health to yourself and nearby players.

name: Elemental Tap
description: Tap into the mana of the earth, restoring 10 Mana <color=#39CCFF>plus</color> 10% of your Maximum Mana to yourself and nearby players.

name: Expert Crafter
description: Your leadership and skills at crafting increase the craft speed of yourself and all players by 20%.

name: Elven Eyes
description: Your elven eyes see much and miss nothing, increasing damage with crossbows by 15%.

name: Primal Nature
description: Your attacks have a chance to restore health. Feel the wild call of battle!

name: Mermaid's Touch
description: Your Mermaid heritage gives you natural fishing skills, increasing the Sweet Spot while landing a fish by 30%.

name: Wish Bottle
description: A wish in a bottle!

name: Ethereal Axe
description: Summons a giant magical axe that swings in a large arc in front of you, dealing damage to trees.

name: Night Forest Wallpaper
description: Wallpaper that captures a forboding forest scape, blanketed in the colors and hues of a deep purple night.

name: Sunrise Forest Wallpaper
description: Wallpaper that captures a forboding forest scape, blanketed in the colors and hues of a deep red morning.

name: Basic Wallpaper
description: A simple wallpaper to spruce up your home's walls.

name: Flower Wallpaper
description: Surround yourself with the beauty of flowers by plastering your walls with them.

name: Withergate Wallpaper
description: Take the spooky vibe of Withergate home with you, and then put it on your walls.

name: Vintage Wallpaper
description: Based on the cottages of the Eastern Region, this wallpaper will give your home a very cozy feel.

name: Earthy Grid Wallpaper
description: This wallpaper mimics the look of clay tiles on your walls.

name: Pink Rosebud Wallpaper
description: Put this on your walls and you'll never go another day without a healthy dose of pink ever again.

name: Purple Grid Wallpaper
description: Your eyes could get lost following the endless corners and turns of this gridded design.

name: Purple Striped Wallpaper
description: It's not the most complicated wallpaper design, but it's so pleasant to look at.

name: Parchment Wallpaper

name: Retro Striped Wallpaper

name: Blue Diamond Wallpaper

name: Bunny Wallpaper
description: A wallpaper that is certain to quell anyone's doubt in your obsession with the bunny lifestyle.

name: Purple Vintage Wallpaper

name: Withergate Royalty Wallpaper

name: Purple Gold Arch Wallpaper

name: Gray Brick Wallpaper

name: Stained Glass Purple Wallpaper
description: Various minerals were mixed into the sand of this glass to produce this striking color.

name: Navy Withergate Wallpaper
description: Take the spooky vibe of Withergate home with you, and then put it on your walls.

name: Art Deco Purple Wallpaper
description: Sleek and industrial, a very classy wallpaper.

name: Withergate Apartment Wallpaper
description: Just like the wallpaper they use in the Withergate apartments, now you can have it in your own home!

name: Nel'Vari Treehouse Wallpaper
description: Wallpaper that has been diligently hand-painted to resemble tree bark, it looks almost like the real thing.
